    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ Lord, Thy ho-ly Mar-tyrs, since they had for-got--ten all that is but earth---ly, com-plete---ly set at___ nought__ most bit-ter___ tor---ments for the e--ter-nal life to come.__ Now_____ they have in-her-it--ed that__ life a-bove;__ where-----fore, they re-joice__ with__ the an-gel-ic hosts.__ In-cline to their en-treat-----ies,__ grant--ing__ un-to__ Thy__ peo----ple great mer-cy through____ their____ prayers."
